  "title": "M&E BIM MODELLER CUM DRAFTER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>• Produce M&amp;E BIM model deliverables for design, documentation and fabrication purpose.</p>\n<p>• Ensure that M&amp;E BIM models are delivered with professionalism (Quality, due diligence and timeliness)</p>\n<p>• Prepare models for Clash Detection Coordination</p>\n<p>• Identify issues for BIM Managers where discrepancies occur during design production.</p>\n<p>• Ensure BIM models are modelled with the correct BIM parameters and attributes for BIM assisted Quantification, 4D simulation</p>\n<p>• The BIM modeller’s overall responsibility is to create BIM content and extracting production documents for the purpose of delivering a BIM assisted project.</p>\n<p>• Produce accurate AUTOCAD and REVIT BIM drawing according to project requirements;</p>\n<p>• To complete documentation from detailed engineering drawings, construction drawings, shop drawings, and as-built drawings, and produce drawing sets</p>\n<p>• They assist BIM Coordinators in creating BIM models for projects. Assist in building basic BIM libraries.</p>\n<p>• Preparation of M&amp;E shop drawings, and As-built drawing;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Diploma/Degree in Electrical/Mechanical Engineering;</p>\n<p>• Preferrably with Certificate from BCA BIM modelling course or equivalent</p>\n<p>• Minimum 3 years of work experience in M&amp;E field, preferably in building construction industry;</p>\n<p>• Proficient in AUTOCAD and MEP Revit software</p>\n<p>• Able to work independently under stress and pressure;</p>\n<p>• Good work attitude with passion and drive</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested candidates please email resume to <a href=\"mailto:Career@kah.com.sg\"><strong>Career@kah.com.sg</strong></a>. </p>\n<p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
